recommend keep-going -- the growth edge is now walked once, not only named; Sala B0 is green and in the suite. The honest next step that keeps the edge is Pool P0 (host the Open Ask loop over Caravan's capability table), which unblocks Sala B1 (live carriage) -- one real lap at a time, ship before naming the next.
